Step 1: Start Jenkins
Open browser:
http://localhost:8080

Step 2: Create Jenkins Job
On Jenkins Dashboard:
New Item
Enter:Maven-CI
Select:Freestyle Project
Click:OK

Step 3
Under:
Source Code Management
Select:Git
Paste your GitHub repository URL:
https://github.com/Hanuaditya/devops_prg6_git.git
Branch:*/main

step 4: Add Maven Build Step
Scroll to: Build
Click: Add Build Step
Choose: Invoke top-level Maven targets
Goals: clean package
Click:Advanced
Enter:myapp/pom.xml

step5: Publish Test Results
Scroll to: Post Build Actions
Choose: Publish JUnit Test Result Report
Enter:myapp/target/surefire-reports/*.xml
click save

step6:
Click:Build Now
